Package nl.fcdonders.fieldtrip.bufferserver.network

Class NetworkProtocol

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.fcdonders.fieldtrip.bufferserver.network.NetworkProtocol
  • public class NetworkProtocol
extends java.lang.Object
    An impementation of the fieldtrip realtime network protocol. Provides a number of abstract methods that can be used to decode/unwrap incoming communication. And a number of functions that can be used to send outgoing data.
    Author:
    Wieke Kanters
